      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a feeling though. i've been noticing it's always the same kind of geometric, repetitive stuff. like, if you look into \"subliminal visual priming\" or how certain frequencies of patterns can trigger specific brain waves, it's actually a huge thing in marketing. i'm not saying the shirt is magic, but why would they make these specific patterns so ubiquitous if they didn't serve a purpose? it feels way too calculated to be a coincidence.",
